Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.56,0:02:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明 已经做好心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是却好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者 我来告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我教给你们的战斗方式的名称
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是消耗战！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是忍受疼痛而战的战术！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是战斗的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是存在的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是对消失的恐惧！祝福者！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想留在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的攻击出现了停顿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类陆续突破防线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前进！别放过这个机会！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要像这样 成为这个岛就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要拥抱你们大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像妈妈那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 我要和这个岛融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们回归虚无！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快闪开！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:05:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢生存吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 现在存在于此的喜悦 祝福者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是C点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见 用锁刃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是用于让人类和祝福者共存的…数据…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也太多了吧 要溢出的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 大部分都正在往某个地方发送
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙宫岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北极方面传来了数据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alvis所有服务器及乌尔德之泉自动接收了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太庞大了…
