Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为同化的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体的同化现象复发了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要接受治疗 一定能康复
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回岛上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mir行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在！开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面出现敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的同化开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的Mir想和天空连接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和从大气层外进攻的祝福者一起覆盖整个地球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化Mk.Ⅶ的武器向它射击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见你来扣扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Mk.Sein的能量以最大功率发射出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则一骑的身体会撑不住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对它们而言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那或许是唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是最后的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个Mir也和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了证明生与死 存在与虚无是二者一体循环往复的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会诞生于这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到另一个Mir那里去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在纷纷坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沟口先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认法芙娜部队全员平安！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 他们成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下…起风了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内核和岛融为了一体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是风…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们马上就能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Nicht？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mir以自己的死给予了祝福者作为个体的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去大家都会被牵连
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来 远见！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要——！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑！一骑!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点 同步并没有中断！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要缺了一个人 同步就会丧失机能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你在战斗前告诉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在于任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在与虚无正在交战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在于任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是将一切归于虚无的祝福者式的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在现实世界中 我们多半已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…还在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 还在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的太空舰队和大气层内的祝福者的内核
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们都在燃烧和下坠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发动之前就整舰被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎还完好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和机体的构造同化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把控制权移交给系统
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离陆之后我来操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞得起来吗 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:17:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mir理解了生命的循环
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是乙姬…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是她本人再生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是对原型的复制
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是偏离了生命本质的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本是乙姬的个体转生成了新的生命…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 她一定会作为内核长大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有朝一日来与我们对话的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们以这个岛为希望 一直存在于此地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要继续前进 就能回到岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了最后关头 还是被你搭救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我教给了祝福者疼痛和存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也了解了他们的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解了存在与虚无的循环
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在与…虚无的循环？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经几乎都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回 回到岛上去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起接受治疗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这么做吧 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再过不久就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士 你说什么呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说 总士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去一趟祝福者的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再次创造出自己的实体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道要花多少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直至有朝一日再度重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士——!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅶ应急检修完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可以出击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员的精神状态也很稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第7龙穴 开门！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜 Mk.Ⅶ 出击！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（OP-EP26ver.）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:21:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里 等着你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:21:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我领悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:22:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便生存充满痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会选择存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.58,0:23:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与你再度相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 我一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到你所在的地方
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（END）
